data.value: SELECT P.ID_PROYECTO AS ID_PROYECTO_PARAM, P.NAME_PROYECTO AS PROYECTO, U.USER_NAME AS SOLICITANTE, UA.USER_NAME AS AUTORIZADO, M.TEXT_ID AS MUESTRA, M.CHANGED_ON AS FECHA, M.OBSERVACIONES AS OBSERVACIONES, PL.NAME_PLANTA AS LOTE, C.NAME_CLIENTE AS CLIENTE, M.RECD_DATE AS 'FECHA RECEPCIÓN', A.ALIAS_NAME AS ANALISIS, CASE WHEN R.RESULT_NUMBER < TRY_CAST(SUBSTRING(AD.CLAMP_LOW, 2, LEN(AD.CLAMP_LOW)-1) AS FLOAT) THEN AD.CLAMP_LOW WHEN R.RESULT_NUMBER > TRY_CAST(SUBSTRING(AD.CLAMP_HIGH, 2, LEN(AD.CLAMP_HIGH)-1) AS FLOAT) THEN AD.CLAMP_HIGH ELSE CAST(CAST(R.RESULT_NUMBER AS FLOAT) AS VARCHAR(20)) END AS VALOR FROM PROYECTO P INNER JOIN MUESTRA M ON P.ID_PROYECTO = M.PROJECT INNER JOIN PLANTA PL ON M.ID_PLANTA = PL.ID_PLANTA INNER JOIN CLIENTE C ON C.ID_CLIENTE = M.ID_CLIENTE INNER JOIN USUARIO U ON M.LOGIN_BY = U.ID_USER INNER JOIN USUARIO UA ON M.REVIEWER = UA.ID_USER INNER JOIN RESULTADO R ON M.ID_SAMPLE = R.ID_SAMPLE INNER JOIN ANALISIS_DETALLE AD ON R.ID_ANALYSIS = AD.ID_ANALISIS AND R.ID_COMPONENT = AD.ID_COMPONENT INNER JOIN ANALISIS A ON AD.ID_ANALISIS = A.ID_ANALISIS WHERE AD.REPORTABLE = 1 AND M.STATUS = 21
